				\begin{document}$$P_{I \to C}^{Res} > P_{I \to C}^{Vul}$$\end{document}PI→CRes>PI→CVul.1 Asymptomatic infectives (A) always show complete recovery, i.e. \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
