As mentioned in the earlier section, we implement random seeding of infection in our simulated community to mimic the arrival of migrants. This factor is given by the transfer matric \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
